title: Sex Lies & Fruit Flies - Paullina Nichols
description: I knew I was risking my life and his, but I couldn't be without him. Ever since he pierced me with those beautiful blue eyes, I hadn't been the same. I'd just escaped a miserable existence and started anew. I was jeopardizing it all. I knew my people back home would kill him for pursuing me, but it didn't matter. He said I was worth dying for. Human men with Aerwyna women were needed for one thing and one thing only, to impregnate us. I didn't care and neither did he. Nothing compared to being wrapped in him. He was my protector, my lover, and my friend. Live and let go or love and face death. We chose love
